	"档案柜要求给你的每句话填写“遗产来源”。原创一栏已经被涂黑。你填什么？": "The archive cabinet requires a \"legacy source\" for every sentence you speak. The Original field has been blacked out. What will you enter?",
	"抄写员把表格转过来，背面密密麻麻都是尚未发生的引用。": "The Copyist turned the form over. Its back was crowded with citations that had not happened yet.",
	"填写此刻": "Enter this moment",
	"来源写此刻；这句话也许借过词，但犹豫是我自己的。": "Write this moment as the source. The sentence may borrow words, but the hesitation is mine.",
	"拒绝来源": "Refuse a source",
	"我不替活着的话伪造祖先，请把这一栏保持空白。": "I will not forge an ancestor for a living sentence. Leave this field blank.",
	"登记污染": "Register corruption",
	"标注语言污染；相似不一定是继承，也可能是感染。": "Mark it as language corruption. Resemblance is not always inheritance; it may be infection.",
	"盖章机说，未被塔收录的句子不算存在。抄写员把印章递给你。": "The stamping machine says a sentence not registered by the tower does not exist. The Copyist offers you the stamp.",
	"抄写员收回没有落下的印章，把你的句子夹进两页制度之间。": "The Copyist took back the unused stamp and slipped your sentence between two pages of procedure.",
	"不盖印章": "Do not stamp it",
	"存在不该由塔批准；让这句话带着空白离开档案。": "Existence should not require the tower's approval. Let this sentence leave the archive with its blank intact.",
	"盖在边缘": "Stamp the edge",
	"只盖在纸的边缘，证明制度碰过它，却没有拥有它。": "Stamp only the edge, proving the system touched it without owning it.",
	"改写条款": "Rewrite the clause",
	"先把条款改成“说出即存在”，再决定是否需要印章。": "First rewrite the clause as \"spoken means existing.\" Then decide whether a stamp is needed.",
	"盖章机吞掉了句子的主语。抄写员拉下断电杆，本次登记以空白中止。": "The stamping machine swallowed the sentence's subject. The Copyist cut the power, ending this registration in a blank.",
	"塔里的发射机没有接线，信徒却说每晚都能收到圣歌。你认为声音从哪里来？": "The transmitter in the tower has no wiring, yet the believer receives a hymn every night. Where do you think the sound comes from?",
	"无名信徒仰头辨认那段旋律，塔窗一层接一层地亮错顺序。": "The Nameless Believer looked up to identify the melody. The tower windows lit floor by floor in the wrong order.",
	"来自人群": "From the crowd",
	"也许是人群在塔下互相复述，最后忘了第一句话属于谁。": "Perhaps the crowd repeats itself below the tower until everyone forgets who owned the first sentence.",
	"来自遗产": "From the legacy",
	"遗产梗会自己寻找嗓子，圣歌只是它们同时借到人的时刻。": "Legacy memes seek out voices. A hymn is simply the moment they all borrow people at once.",
	"来自静电": "From static",
	"没有信号时，静电也会被当成启示；先别急着跪下。": "With no signal, even static can pass for revelation. Do not kneel just yet.",
	"信徒请你献出一句不会污染别人的话，作为进入上层的圣歌。": "The believer asks you to offer a sentence that will not corrupt anyone else, a hymn for entering the floor above.",
	"无名信徒没有唱你的句子，只把它安静地留在门外。塔门第一次自己开了。": "The Nameless Believer did not sing your sentence. They left it quietly outside, and the tower door opened by itself for the first time.",
	"保留疑问": "Keep a question",
	"我只能献出一个问题：我们是否允许别人不回答。": "I can offer only a question: do we allow other people not to answer?",
	"归还名字": "Return the names",
	"把每个人的名字还给本人，不把它们编进共同的副歌。": "Return every name to its owner. Do not weave them into a shared refrain.",
	"献出停顿": "Offer a pause",
	"我献出一句话结束后的停顿，让下一人有地方开口。": "I offer the pause after a sentence ends, so the next person has room to speak.",
	"圣歌突然只剩同一个梗。无名信徒停止合唱，塔门在污染扩散前合上。": "The hymn suddenly collapsed into one repeated meme. The Nameless Believer stopped singing, and the tower door shut before the corruption spread.",
	"旧帖显示这里“信号满格”，可所有回复都写着十年后发送。你要点开哪一条？": "The old post shows \"FULL SIGNAL,\" but every reply is marked as sent ten years from now. Which one will you open?",
	"旧帖目击者滑动屏幕，日期栏像坏掉的电梯一样上下跳动。": "The Old-Post Witness scrolled. The date field lurched up and down like a broken elevator.",
	"最早回复": "Earliest reply",
	"打开最早的一条，看看是谁先把未来误认成了遗产。": "Open the earliest one and see who first mistook the future for a legacy.",
	"未发回复": "Unsent reply",
	"打开那条尚未发送的，也许它还来得及换一种说法。": "Open the one not yet sent. It may still have time to say things differently.",
	"关闭帖子": "Close the post",
	"先关掉帖子；无信号时，时间不该假装自己已经上传。": "Close the post first. With no signal, time should not pretend it has already uploaded itself.",
	"最后一条回复只有一个梗框，里面空着。帖子问：要把今天的哪个词留给过去？": "The final reply contains only an empty Meme Frame. The post asks: which word from today will you leave to the past?",
	"旧帖目击者没有截屏。空框自行保存，又把今天完整地退还给你。": "The Old-Post Witness took no screenshot. The empty frame saved itself, then returned today to you intact.",
	"留下存在": "Leave existence",
	"留下“存在”；过去需要知道我们没有只活成引用。": "Leave \"existence.\" The past should know we did not live only as quotations.",
	"留下无信号": "Leave no signal",
	"留下“无信号”；让未来明白沉默也可能是线路断了。": "Leave \"no signal.\" Let the future know silence can also mean a broken connection.",
	"什么不留": "Leave nothing",
	"什么都不留；过去不该提前继承我们尚未说完的话。": "Leave nothing. The past should not inherit words we have not finished speaking.",
	"帖子开始自动复制你尚未说出的词。旧帖目击者拔掉电源，屏幕仍亮在中断处。": "The post began copying words you had not spoken yet. The Old-Post Witness pulled the plug, but the screen remained lit at the interruption.",

	# Signal Merchant dialogue and choices.
